docs {
  # Trigger Food Reminder (Manual)

  Immediately sends the weekly food reminder push notification to active
  food subscribers who are located in **Bangalore** and have a registered push subscription.
  Users in other locations are excluded.

  ## Access
  Restricted to DeptHOD of HR or Food Committee only.
  Returns 403 for all other roles.

  ## Notification content
  - Title: "🍱 Food Reminder"
  - Body: "Have you sorted next week's food? Tap 'Yes' if you're all set, or 'No' to update your preference now."
  - Actions: "Yes, I'm done ✓" (dismiss) | "No, take me there →" (opens food page)
  - requireInteraction: true (stays until user acts)

  ## Automatic schedule
  The same notification fires automatically via cron:
  - Monday    5:00 PM IST (11:30 UTC)
  - Wednesday 5:00 PM IST (11:30 UTC)
  - Saturday  5:00 PM IST (11:30 UTC)

  ## Response
  - `success: true`
  - `target: "all"`
}
